    creative_name VARCHAR(255),
    message TEXT,
    conversion_rate DECIMAL(5,2)
);


CREATE TABLE ad_campaigns (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name VARCHAR(255),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    budget DECIMAL(10,2)
);


CREATE TABLE ad_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    creative_id INT,
    clicks INT,
    conversions INT,
    revenue DECIMAL(15,2)
);
